<form action="welcome.html" target="_blank">
  <label>Email:</label>
  <input type="email" name="email">
  <input type="submit" value="Open in New Tab">
</form>


Explanation:

target="_blank" â†’ opens the result in a new tab.

ğŸ“ 3. enctype Attribute (for File Uploads)
<form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <label>Upload Image:</label>
  <input type="file" name="photo" accept="image/*">
  <input type="submit" value="Upload">
</form>


Explanation:

enctype="multipart/form-data" â†’ required when uploading files.

ğŸ§  4. autocomplete, novalidate
<form action="/login" method="post" autocomplete="on" novalidate>
  <label>Username:</label>
  <input type="text" name="user" autocomplete="username">

  <label>Password:</label>
  <input type="password" name="pass" autocomplete="current-password">

  <input type="submit" value="Login">
</form>


Explanation:

autocomplete="on/off" â†’ browser auto-fills data.

novalidate â†’ disables HTML5 validation.

ğŸ¯ 5. name, value, readonly, disabled
<form>
  <label>Name:</label>
  <input type="text" name="fullname" value="Devendra">

  <label>City:</label>
  <input type="text" value="Kurnool" readonly>

  <label>PIN Code:</label>
  <input type="text" value="518001" disabled>

  <input type="submit">
</form>


Explanation:

readonly â†’ user canâ€™t change but field is sent.

disabled â†’ user canâ€™t change and field is not sent.

âš™ï¸ 6. form Attribute (External Button Control)
<form id="infoForm">
  <label>First Name:</label>
  <input type="text" name="fname">
</form>

<input type="submit" form="infoForm" value="Submit Form">


Explanation:

The submit button is outside the form but linked using form="infoForm".

ğŸ’¡ 7. All-In-One Example
<form action="/submit" method="post" target="_blank"
      enctype="multipart/form-data" autocomplete="on" novalidate>
  <h3>Registration Form</h3>

  <label>Full Name:</label>
  <input type="text" name="fullname" required>

  <label>Email:</label>
  <input type="email" name="email" required>

  <label>Profile Photo:</label>
  <input type="file" name="photo">

  <input type="submit" value="Register">
</form>


Attributes used: action, method, target, enctype, autocomplete, novalidate, required.
